(If Dinobot meant Mosquitor: he shoots acid, not poison.)

::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor yells in rage as Dinobot takes his shots (assuming he was the one 
Dinobot meant) for Tavatron and shoots him. He stumbles back but regains his 
balance.

"I shall kill you too, Maximal!!!" Mosquitor yells as he jumps at Dinobot, 
firing more acid at him.
